[I] A small wrapper library around GtkSourceView for gedit

[T] libgedit-gtksourceview is a small wrapper library around GtkSourceView used
[T] by gedit and related GNOME text editors to provide editing capabilities
[T] with syntax highlighting.

[U] https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/gedit/libgedit-gtksourceview

